title: Let Me Check Your Hymen
itunes:title: Let Me Check Your Hymen
description:
Today on the show we opened up the phone lines to see if our listeners believed if T.I is being over protective with his daughter when it comes to going to the gynecologist with her, to make sure she is still a virgin. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a Florida man who said he was a victim of Voodoo and Angela helped some listeners during "Ask Yee".
